node.person.name: Jason Klein
node.areas_of_interest_freeform:
On Grid Ventures supports the startup and success of B2B and consumer businesses which leverage connectivity technologies to disrupt and improve clearly defined markets.
We look for early stage companies which capitalize  these five advances:
Location-based products, services, and infrastructure;
AI/Machine Learning, particularly when built from large, location-infused data-sets
Marketplaces and e-com
Peer-to-peer networks and network effects, crowd-s
IoT connectivity across devices, places, peo
